        {
            "title": "港股曾跌527點   中芯挫近6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數跌幅超過500點，最多跌527點或2.17%，報23704，現跌508點或2.1%，報23722。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數報8697，踷16點或2.42%，恒生科技指數跌186點或3.08%，報5851點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯國際(00981)跌5.86%，報51.4元 ; 李寧(02331)跌5.68%，報17.6元 ; 聯通(00762)跌4.94%，報9.43元，為表現最差三藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度(09888)升1.82%，報92.45元，為表現最佳藍籌股。 </p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14764977-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c527%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%ad%e8%8a%af%e6%8c%ab%e8%bf%916",
